{"tid":2513531,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"接種疫苗後性慾爆棚　85歲老翁1小時內連戰3女","createTime":"2021-05-02T14:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:36:43.000Z","uid":28114,"like":378,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":80,"replies":[{"pid":"f51bf0c7b50114c492758db4dabdf84c826eeea9","tid":2513531,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:56:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/s6X0GVXbB3DsPYjca66LTFfdREA=/538x302/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6QLFWRPKDZCPDHIGBDV334VGCA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fs6X0GVXbB3DsPYjca66LTFfdREA%3D%2F538x302%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6QLFWRPKDZCPDHIGBDV334VGCA.jpg&h=b6b074b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n許多國家都陸續在施打新冠肺炎疫苗，義大利一名85歲老翁在施打後卻出現特殊的「副作用」，他感覺到自己精力無窮、性慾爆發，結果在宵禁期間外出嫖妓被警察抓包，而且是一小時內兩次，結果總共被罰款1000歐元（約3.4萬元台幣）。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》等媒體報導，義大利目前規定晚上10時至隔天凌晨5時，民眾必須待在家中，除非有工作需要、緊急狀況或健康因素，否則將面臨罰款。但義大利警方發言人西吉斯蒙多（Sigismondo Lettieri）透露，近日有一起奇特的違反宵禁案例，是一名85歲的老翁為了買春，在一小時內就連續被警方開罰兩次。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，老翁上周從蘇連多開車到埃博利買春，因為當地有站街女郎在攬客，老翁便與兩名賣淫女在一輛房車裡面3P嘿咻，結果正好遇到警方巡邏，老翁因違反宵禁規定被罰款；原以為老翁應該就此離去，想不到警方不到一小時後再次巡經該處，發現老翁剛剛嘿咻的房車還在，湊近一看，發現老翁正在和一名賣淫女做愛，於是老翁又因違反宵禁被罰款。<br />\n<br />\n雖然老翁兩度被罰款而失去了1000歐元，但他卻似乎一點都不心疼，他表示<span class=\"red\">「我接種了新冠肺炎疫苗後，整個人精力大增，感覺性慾都要爆棚了」</span>，直呼這個罰款被罰得很值得。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210427/4I3PYQP7LFELRHG2TUJTIBSGYY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210427%2F4I3PYQP7LFELRHG2TUJTIBSGYY%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=5de19618\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210427%2F4I3PYQP7LFELRHG2TUJTIBSGYY%2F&h=fbf7a2c4\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20210427/4I3PYQP7LFELRHG2TUJTIBSGYY/</a>"},{"pid":"a874fc7eb17e1d9cd37020656b3c6f2430a8d6a1","tid":2513531,"uid":28114,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:56:47.000Z","msg":"Italian man violated lockdown to meet prostitutes, blames vaccine<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nypost.com/2021/04/26/italian-man-violated-lockdown-rules-to-meet-call-girls-blames-vax/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2021%2F04%2F26%2Fitalian-man-violated-lockdown-rules-to-meet-call-girls-blames-vax%2F&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtbXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=374499aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://nypost.com/2021/04/26/italian-man-violated-lockdown-rules-to-meet-call-girls-blames-vax/</a>"},{"pid":"dd4bd5612e26a43d9c2adc94429f4f880efc673b","tid":2513531,"uid":28114,"like":239,"dislike":42,"score":197,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"反疫苗撚今次應該都啞口無言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e80a9a9da84f83e0f0a7c15a8efdb8238d5202","tid":2513531,"uid":80564,"like":363,"dislike":3,"score":360,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T14:58:08.000Z","msg":"其實打偉哥定疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6107218128692c5243b8178c9cc8e2483f209c72","tid":2513531,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:00:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c458e214c6ce6b8546cf9c76334848b14eb8aa","tid":2513531,"uid":76310,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:01:15.000Z","msg":"咪住, 佢打邊種先"},{"pid":"23185077fc7af17c6a426ca4ce6acab6e6d24124","tid":2513531,"uid":285514,"like":85,"dislike":0,"score":85,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T15:01:48.000Z","msg":"咁香港啲藍絲老嘢快啲打喇喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3697e5fb0b9229c5c9bfe62ffa566daaf00043","tid":2513531,"uid":350267,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-0